GetAllFreeBusyProviders SOAP Command

Get all free/busy providers

Authorization token required true
Admin Authorization token required true

GetAllFreeBusyProvidersRequest

    <GetAllFreeBusyProvidersRequest /> ## GetAllFreeBusyProvidersRequest

GetAllFreeBusyProvidersResponse

    <GetAllFreeBusyProvidersResponse> ## GetAllFreeBusyProvidersResponse
        (<provider name="{provider-name}" propagate="{propagate-flag} (0|1)"
                       start="{fb-cache-start-time-secs-since-epoch} (long)"
                       end="{fb-cache-end-time-secs-since-epoch} (long)" queue="{queue location}"
                       prefix="{prefix-used-in-zimbra-ForeignPrincipal}" /> ## FreeBusyProviderInfo)*
    </GetAllFreeBusyProvidersResponse>

The following table describes elements and attributes you can define within a <GetAllFreeBusyProvidersResponse> element:

XPath Required / Optional Description

/provider@name Required (only 1) Type:String
Provider name
/provider@propagate Required (only 1) Type:0|1
Propagate flag
/provider@start Required (only 1) Type:long
Free/Busy cache start time in seconds since the epoch
/provider@end Required (only 1) Type:long
Free/Busy cache end time in seconds since the epoch
/provider@queue Required (only 1) Type:String
Queue location
/provider@prefix Required (only 1) Type:String
